title: Baan Namchaa
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Western, Juice bar, Burmese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Run by three Europeans and a Burmese cook, this place is all vegetarian except for a tuna fish sandwich. Located around 50 meters east of the first intersection east of the beach on the northern Ao Yai road.
